{"tid":1739454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[西北撚入］有冇人記得西鐵線啱啱通車嘅時候成日壞車","createTime":"2019-11-19T15:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T23:24:21.000Z","uid":336237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1c75f80291859b76ed618d1d35e52e66efe170","tid":1739454,"uid":336237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"西鐵啱啱通個幾年，基本上每次行雷閃電都會訊號故障<br />\n因為西鐵本身起得高，多架空路段同電纜，所以個天嘅環境對佢好大影響<br />\n我就諗，以前有冇啲仆街人為整停過西鐵呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有喎！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em>西鐵線昨晚故障一度停駛　港鐵懷疑有人放孔明燈惹禍 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPiABAJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPiABAJ.png&h=b159a88e&s={SIZE}\" />hk01-20180925</em><br />\n<br />\n所以千祈<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>亂放孔明燈上天<br />\n一陣唔覺意停半個鐘就成班人喺西鐵站屌哂鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fbfef50eeb6ffb2a9dfdaa03dd3dcd42d2206b","tid":1739454,"uid":336237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"63af70aed6d02103bb70e6d61cf3c0d8e256db77","tid":1739454,"uid":336237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"c3a4831fc84143fc233b7f3d1c5bcec32b3f2f7d","tid":1739454,"uid":336237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"8b733e8357fa095224cff42bba8755cbc7b0f364","tid":1739454,"uid":310982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T23:24:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}